      "code": "import re\nARABIC_DIACRITICS = re.compile(r\"[\\u0610-\\u061A\\u064B-\\u065F\\u06D6-\\u06ED]\")\nTATWEEL = '\\u0640'\n\ndef normalize_arabic(s):\n    s = re.sub(ARABIC_DIACRITICS, '', s)\n    s = s.replace(TATWEEL, '')\n    # unify alef forms\n    s = s.replace('أ', 'ا').replace('إ', 'ا').replace('آ', 'ا')\n    # Ya and Alif Maqsura unify\n    s = s.replace('ى', 'ي')\n    # Ta marbuta to ha? usually not necessary\n    # unify hamza forms\n    s = s.replace('ؤ', 'و').replace('ئ', 'ي').replace('ء', '')\n    # handle small alif madd sign? already removed by diacritics\n    # remove punctuation\n    s = re.sub(r'[^\\u0621-\\u063A\\u0641-\\u064A\\s]', ' ', s)\n    # collapse spaces\n    s = re.sub(r'\\s+', ' ', s).strip()\n    return s\n\nquery = \"قلنا يا نار كوني بردا وسلاما على ابراهيم\"\nnorm_query = normalize_arabic(query)\nnorm_query",
